divs: Sighting DetailsIn my back yard having my morning smoke the sun was not up but the sky had light. A Very Bright Light traveling north to south, no sound moving at a fast rate and disappeared. I tried to get a picture but my settings were off so the image came out dark. you can still see the light but the picture does nothing for the size and brightness I saw. I have never seen anything like it..
Summary: Very Bright Light, no sound moving very fast.
